                        <p>To use this theme you must be running <strong>WordPress 4.5</strong> or higher, <strong>PHP 5.6.20</strong> or higher<!--, and <strong>mysql 5</strong> or higher--> (for <i>Booked</i> plug-in <strong>PHP 7.0 +</strong>). If you use hosting with limited resources (for example GoDaddy and other lowcost shared hosting providers), you may experience issues with one-click demo data installation feature.</p>

