                        <p>A few recommendations on how to use Child Theme from AxiomThemes: </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                Almost all files from the main theme can be replaced in the  theme. It doesn&rsquo;t concern only .php-files
                                with templates and basic logics, but also both .js, .css files from respective folders and files with
                                images, icons etc.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                If you want to change some of the theme-related functions or to add new ones, copy/add all the required functions into 'functions.php' in the &quot;pets-grooming-child&quot; folder. If our
